Elf, Dwarf, Halfling, Human first names from Dungeon World
Elf surnames from: http://www.candlekeep.com/library/articles/elven_names.htm
Halfling surnames from: http://www.angelfire.com/rpg/annwn/nameshalf.html
Native names from The Land of Imagination
